<REFEX REG08-TYPE="pronoun" EMPHATIC="yes" HEAD="rel-pron" CASE="nominative">which itself</REFEX>
</ALT-REFEX>
</REF>
 was the highest point in any state of the United States until Texas joined the union in 1845. The nearest higher point on the North American continent is Harney Peak in the Black Hills of South Dakota. 
